<l n="d">tāvat kīrtti<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied> sthireya<supplied reason="omitted">ṃ</supplied> bhajatu śubhakarīsatsutaṁ puṣyanāmna<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied></l>
